==評論==
在重建高郵湖堤壩出了大力的[[美南長老會|美南長老會]]傳教士[[何伯葵|何伯葵]]，其孫Steve Harnsberger在2007年寫道「1931年這場水災死的人比[[2004年印度洋海嘯|2004年印度洋海嘯]]多15倍，但幾乎沒人對此事留下隻言片語。歷史只記得當年的其他災難——中國當年忙在打國共內戰（註：[[第三次江西剿共战争|第三次江西剿共战争]]），日本忙着侵略東北（註：1931年[[九一八事变|九一八事变]]），世界忙着[[大蕭條|大蕭條]]。」<ref name="come">{{cite web|title=The Great Floods Of 1931 At Gaoyou: August 26, 1931 - The Floods Come|author=Steve Harnsberger|publisher=AboutGaoyou.com|date=2007-09-25|url=http://www.aboutgaoyou.com/history/floods/the_floods.aspx|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200510130325/http://www.aboutgaoyou.com/history/floods/the_floods.aspx|archivedate=2020-05-10|quote=The 1931 flood killed 15 times the number of people lost in the Indonesian tsunamis of December 2004, and yet scarcely a word has been written of it. History focused instead on other disasters that year. China’s attention was on a civil war between the Communists and Nationalists; the Japanese were invading in the North, while the world was deep into the Great Depression.|access-date=2020-05-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

